generated_description: ho shin sool is a mixed martial arts and fitness center located in sault ste. marie, ontario. founded on august 19, 1998, by jim liguori, the club offers a comprehensive range of martial arts programs including traditional martial arts, muay thai, sambo/jiu-jitsu, and mma. known for its strong traditional martial arts program, ho shin sool was the first club in sault ste. marie to introduce mma and sambo, and it was also the first to participate in an mma event. the center is recognized for its certified muay thai instructor and highest ranking sambo instructor in the region. ho shin sool emphasizes a balance between fitness and self-defense, providing a fun and safe environment with a focus on hard work, dedication, and respect among its members.
